c: 16
v: 80
t: "Era Katonda yabateerawo mu mayumba gammwe obuwummuliro, era naabateerawo mu maliba gebisolo amayumba agabanguyira lwe muba mutambudde ne lwe muba temutambudde, ate nabaggira mu byoya bye ndiga ne bye ngamiya ne mu bye mbuzi ebyokukozesa era nga byakweyagala kwa mmwe okumala akabanga"